title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 - Nov 26 2021
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 - Nov 26 2021
description:
Biden issues covid travel bans from Africa. Friday Friend Alex Berenson joins Buck to talk about new covid Omicron variant. What's Fauci's plan -- to keep giving the world boosters in perpetuity? Where is the fact-check on Fauci's lies? Seth Rogen goes viral after shrugging off Los Angeles car burglaries: "It’s called living in a big city." Buck's eScooter was stolen after Thanksgiving dinner with his family. Former NYPD calls in to give Buck tips on filing a police report.
